<h2 class="bold font-l">Akutagawa's "help".</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Akutagawa (grudgingly) agrees to help Atsushi. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MathematiciansAnswer" class='trope-example-link'>Mathematician's Answer</a></p>
